name: Needocs
tag_list: documents, ebooks, download, upload, templates, letters, presentations, thesis, cv, resume
overview:
Needocs is a marketplace of professional documents & ebooks.

Needocs offers a wide range of documents, templates, presentations, studies to professionals, individuals and students.

Needocs allows individuals to publish and sell their value added content and to benefit from an attractive remuneration.

The website’s social media options allow publishers to communicate efficiently on their activities.
